data.description: WELCOME HOME! This move-in ready, single family home will amaze you the moment you walk through the double front doors. You'll be greeted by a 2-story foyer, with a formal dining room and extra living area to your left and right. The main floor also has a single bedroom and full bathroom. The gourmet kitchen includes a large island for serving and entertaining, and opens right into the living room. Upstairs you'll find the oversized primary suite, with a large seating/flex space attached. The beautiful primary suite bathroom is equipped with a soaking tub, oversized shower, two separate vanities, and a walk-in closet. You will also find 3 additional bedrooms, a loft space, and laundry room on the upper level. The fenced in backyard is a field of potential, with enough space to add a pool or an ADU, and still have yard to spare. And let's not forget it's the only home in the neighborhood with a 4 car garage! You don't want to miss out on this one!!
